dquo;ï¼‰ï¼šå°†æ¯”ç‰¹å¸å…‘æ¢æˆè²äºšç‰¹è´§å¸ã€‚</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>åœ¨è¿™ä¸¤ç§æƒ…å†µä¸‹ï¼Œä½ å¿…é¡»è¾“å…¥æ¯”ç‰¹å¸çš„é‡‘é¢å‡ºå”®æˆ–è´­ä¹°ï¼Œå¹¶é€‰æ‹©&quot;è²äºšç‰¹è´§å¸&quot;æŽ¥æ”¶/å–å‡ºã€‚å½“æ‚¨å•å‡»æŒ‰é’®ï¼Œä¸‹è®¢å•ï¼Œæ‚¨å°†çœ‹åˆ°æ‚¨çš„è®¢å•çš„æ€»ç»“ã€‚ç„¶åŽï¼Œæ‚¨å¯ä»¥å†³å®šè¦ç¡®è®¤æˆ–è¿”å›žè®¢è´­é¡µé¢ã€‚</p>\r\n\r\n<p>å¦‚æžœé€‰æ‹©ä»¥<strong>å¸‚åœºä»·æ ¼è´­ä¹°/å–å‡º</strong>ï¼Œ<span style=\"line-height: 20.7999992370605px;\">[exchange_name]</span> å°†æ ¹æ®çŽ°è¡Œå¸‚åœºä»·æ ¼çš„æµ®åŠ¨è‡ªåŠ¨è°ƒæ•´æ‚¨çš„è®¢å•ä»·æ ¼ã€‚</p>\r\n','',''),(37,'how-to-register','How Does It Work?','Â¿CÃ³mo funciona?','<h2>How Does <strong>[exchange_name]</strong> Work?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>To start trading bitcoins on [exchange_name], simply go to the <a href=\"register.php\">registration</a> page and fill in a brief registration form (5 fields). Then log in with the user name and password&nbsp;that you received in your mail and you are set!</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Bitcoin Funding</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>You can fund your account with Bitcoin by visiting the&nbsp;<a href=\"deposit.php\">deposit page</a>&nbsp;and following the instructions. You can also manage and obtain alternative Bitcoin addresses for your account by visiting the&nbsp;<a href=\"bitcoin-addresses.php\">bitcoin addresses</a>&nbsp;page. You may only obtain one new address every 24 hours.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Fiat Currency Funding</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>All fiat currency is handled through your own private bank account in <a href=\"http://www.cryptocapital.co/\" target=\"_blank\">Crypto Capital</a>. Opening an account is a quick process that will allow you to hold up to <strong>30 different fiat currencies</strong> under one roof! Each account comes with its own IBAN number and can be used in other cryptocurrency-related businesses without having to go through verification again.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After you have set up and funded your Crypto Capital&nbsp;account, you can link it to your [exchange_name] account by visiting the&nbsp;<a href=\"bank-accounts.php\">bank accounts</a>&nbsp;page. Just enter the number of your Crypto Capital&nbsp;account, and the funding link will be established.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Once you have followed these steps, you can fund your [exchange_name] account by visiting the&nbsp;<a href=\"deposit.php\">deposit page</a>&nbsp;and follow&nbsp;the instructions.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Order Entry</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>At the moment there are three types of orders: <strong>MARKET</strong>, <strong>STOP</strong> and <strong>LIMIT</strong>.&nbsp;All three can be used to enter or exit the market.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Orders @&nbsp;<strong>MARKET</strong> will be assigned to the best <strong>BID</strong>&nbsp;or the best <strong>ASK</strong>.</li>\r\n	<li>The order entry&nbsp;ticket is simple yet versatile and will offer up a confirmation screen before it goes to the market.</li>\r\n	<li>Open orders can then be easily edited or canceled on the <a href=\"open-orders.php\">open orders page</a>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n','<h2>&iquest;C&oacute;mo funciona <b>[exchange_name]</b>?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Para comenzar a comprar y vender bitcoins en [exchange_name], ingrese a la <a href=\"es/registro.php\">p&aacute;gina de registro</a> y complete el breve formulario (s&oacute;lo 5 campos). Luego, ingrese a su cuenta con el n&uacute;mero de usuario y la contrase&ntilde;a que recibir&aacute; en su correo electr&oacute;nico.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Obtenci&oacute;n de fondos en Bitcoin</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Puede enviar bitcoins a su cuenta ingresando a la <a href=\"deposit.php\">p&aacute;gina de dep&oacute;sitos</a> y siguiendo las instrucciones. Puede administrar las direcciones Bitcoin de su cuenta en la p&aacute;gina de <a href=\"bitcoin-addresses.php\">direcciones Bitcoin</a>. Se puede obtener una nueva direcci&oacute;n cada 24 horas.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Obtenci&oacute;n de fondos en monedas fiduciarias</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"es\"><span class=\"hps\">Toda</span> <span class=\"hps\">moneda fiduciaria</span> <span class=\"hps\">se maneja</span> <span class=\"hps\">a trav&eacute;s de su</span> <span class=\"hps\">propia cuenta bancaria</span> <span class=\"hps\">privada en</span> <a href=\"https://cryptocapital.co\"><span class=\"hps\">Crypto</span> <span class=\"hps\">capital</span></a><span>.</span> <span class=\"hps\">Abrir una cuenta es</span> <span class=\"hps\">un proceso r&aacute;pido</span> <span class=\"hps\">que</span> <span class=\"hps\">le permitir&aacute;</span> <span class=\"hps\">almacenar hasta</span> <span class=\"hps\">30</span> <span class=\"hps\">monedas fiduciarias</span> <span class=\"hps\">diferentes</span> <span class=\"hps\">bajo un mismo techo</span><span>!</span> <span class=\"hps\">Cada cuenta</span> <span class=\"hps\">viene con su</span> <span class=\"hps\">propio n&uacute;mero</span> <span class=\"hps\">IBAN</span> <span class=\"hps\">y se puede utilizar</span> <span class=\"hps\">en</span> <span class=\"hps\">otros negocio</span> <span class=\"hps\">de Criptodivisa</span><span class=\"hps\"></span>s <span class=\"hps\">sin</span> <span class=\"hps\">tener que pasar por</span> <span class=\"hps\">el proceso de <span class=\"short_text\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"es\"><span class=\"hps\">verificaci&oacute;n </span></span></span><span class=\"hps\">nuevamente.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Una vez que haya creado su cuenta en Crypto Capital y le haya transferido fondos, podr&aacute; vincularlo con su cuenta de [exchange_name] visitando la p&aacute;gina de <a href=\"bank-accounts.php\">cuentas bancarias</a>. S&oacute;lo ingrese su n&uacute;mero de cuenta Crypto Capital y el vinculo se establecer&aacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Finalizado este breve proceso, siga las instrucciones en la <a href=\"deposit.php\">p&aacute;gina de dep&oacute;sitos</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Creaci&oacute;n de &oacute;rdenes</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Por el momento, existe